    <hr class="between-sections">

    <!--Section: Where We Get The Clothes-->
    <section class="section">
        <h1 class="section-heading wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.2s">Where We Get The Clothes</h1>

        <p class="section-description wow fadeIn" data-wow-delay="0.4s">
            We get them all from <strong>you</strong>! All of the items we give come from public donations or are purchased using the money <strong>you</strong> donate.
            We accept <strong>gently used</strong> clothing, shoes, pajamas, coats, hats, and gloves in all children and adult sizes
            (styled appropriately for teens). We also accept socks and underwear donations <strong>new</strong> in their package.
        </p>
